parameters:
Dining Hall Lady: Participating in or watching the arena is
all about stamina! If you're going, make sure to eat well
beforehand!

Cafeteria Staff: Please place your order at the counter! We
have plenty of energizing dishes!

Deliveryman: This place is a standing eatery, but the taste
is good and cheap. It's the best. With this job, I don't
have much time to spend on meals either.

Female Pianist: It's often drowned out by the hustle and
bustle, but I'm happy that I can perform for the heroes of
the arena in this city.

Male Worker: If only I had a bit more strength, I could
also excel in the arena.

Bartender: Welcome to this exciting town. The taste of the
drink after watching a match is exceptional.

Noblewoman: This is an oasis in the bustling city, although
it becomes even more chaotic at night.

History-loving customer: The arena that was given the name
of the resilient king Pizuma is so magnificent that it's
hard to believe it's an old building.

Happy customer: I came all the way to Jinami for
sightseeing! The Pizuma Arena is worth seeing even from a
distance, isn't it?

Depressed man: My favorite warrior lost again today... They
have the talent, but lack the courage... What a waste.
